   Bush Plan for Deposit Insurance Shifts
   Risk From Taxpayer to Banks, Depositors
   ----
   By Paulette Thomas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/27/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A2
</SO>
